- invalid num of args:
./pipex files/infile "cat" "grep c"
./pipex files/infile "cat" "grep c" files/outfile lel

- invalid files:
./pipex files/invalid "cat" "grep c" files/outfile
./pipex files/infile "cat" "grep c" files/
./pipex files/ "cat" "grep c" files/outfile

- invalid args:
./pipex files/infile "cadt" "grep c" files/outfile
./pipex files/infile "cat" "grepd c" files/outfile
./pipex files/infile "cat -dsf" "gred -ddf c" files/outfile
./pipex files/infile "" "grep c" files/outfile
./pipex files/infile "cadt" "" files/outfile
./pipex files/infile "" "" files/outfile

- invalid files and args:
./pipex files/invalid "cadt" "grep c" files/outfile
./pipex files/infile "cat" "grepd c" files/
./pipex files/ "cat -dsf" "gred -ddf c" files/outfile
./pipex files/invalid "" "grep c" files/outfile
./pipex files/infile "cadt" "" files/
./pipex files/ "" "" files/outfile

- invalid order:
./pipex "cat" files/infile "grep c" files/outfile
./pipex "cat" "grep c" files/infile  files/outfile
./pipex files/infile files/outfile "cat" "grep c"
./pipex files/infile "cat" "grep c" files/outfile "cat" "grep c"

- other cmds + invalid cmds...
